@node Changes1 " Changes"
@{b}@{" Small Magic  ()" SYSTEM "run >NIL: multiview SmallMagic.Demo"}  Changes@{ub} 
              @{"  " LINK}  Finally, a new release of SmallMagic. A new attempt to                           
              @{"  " LINK}  trike back at the  competition. So lets have a look at
              @{"  " LINK}  what has changes since the previous release.
              @{"  " LINK}
              @{"  " LINK}  Icons -I cleaned up most  of the icons (check out the
              @{"  " LINK}         much  improved  dithering  on the  preferences
              @{"  " LINK}         icons for example)
              @{"  " LINK}        -I completed a new set of  commodity icons (all
              @{"  " LINK}         the commodities I use are now iconised).
              @{"  " LINK}        -The size of the  system icons  has changed  to
              @{"  " LINK}         match those in the tools directory.
Introduction  @{"()" LINK Introduction}        -The AppIcons as used by MUI, Mtool and KingCon
Requirements  @{"()" LINK Requirements}         are now the  same size as standard  disk Icons
Installation  @{"()" LINK Installation}         so the look better (check out the demo).          
Distribution  @{"()" LINK Distribution}        -Some  Picasso icons have  been added to  Small
The  Credits  @{"()" LINK Credits}         Magic. They can be found spreaded over all the
              @{"  " LINK}         directories.
              @{"  " LINK}        -The dockicons  have been improved and new ones
              @{"  " LINK}         have been added. 
   June 1995  @{"()" LINK Dockbrushes} <-NEW  -The invention (I think) of DockPictures.      
@endnode

@node Distribution " Copyrights & Distribution "
@{b}@{" Small Magic  ()" SYSTEM "run >NIL: multiview SmallMagic.Demo"} Copyrights & Distribution@{ub}
